                <p><emph>Edd.</emph> <bibl><ref target="#b1554">Platon 1959</ref>, p. 377</bibl>; 
                    <bibl><ref target="#b213">Bultrighini 1993</ref>, p. 107</bibl> (= <bibl type="main_edition"><ref target="#bib5"><title>SEG</title></ref> 45.1314 <ptr type="phi" target="202222"/></bibl>).</p>
